% ====================================================================
% test_bestagon_proto_ai_v2_perf.trx -- run examples/bestagon-proto/
% proto-ai-v2-perf.trx via the tests/ harness.
% ====================================================================
%
% Thin wrapper: loads proto-ai-v2-perf.trx (Phase 0.6D: AI v2 perf-
% budget prototype per GDD section 14), which runs three evaluation
% modes on Standard + Epic fixtures and writes the verdict to
% examples/bestagon-proto/out/ai-v2-perf.md.
%
% Functional regression only -- this test asserts the proto runs to
% completion without error; the actual budget verdict numbers are NOT
% asserted here because absolute wall-clock varies by build (debug vs
% prod) and host.  The proto's stdout summary table is the primary
% artifact; the markdown verdict file is the secondary artifact.
%
% Runs on default 1 MB VM via per-phase save/restore brackets.
% On debug build: ~30-60s.  On prod build (./trix.opt): ~5-7s.
% ====================================================================

(examples/bestagon-proto/proto-ai-v2-perf.trx) run
(__test_ok__) =
